Minimal base environment

A base OpenBSD install includes
Standard unix utilities and services
Toolchain
Full documentation

Benefits
Reduces the risk of hidden dependencies
OS patches/upgrades easily separated from toolchain mainenance/upgrades

Additional development tools and execution environments in ports tree.


